pr_title: Updated the directory structure and Makefile
pr_body:
Related Issue: #27, #28 

With this PR, devs can run
   - `make build` and get frontend, operator, pod-simulator, and helm chart build
   - `make generate` and get CRDs, zz files generate and Helm chart will get updated too
   - `make lint` and frontend, operator, pod-simulator, and helm chart will be linted
